## ‚òÅÔ∏è Google Cloud Skills Boost ‚Äî *Prompt Design in Vertex AI*

### üß≠ Overview

This course introduces the concepts and practices of **prompt engineering** within Google Cloud‚Äôs **Vertex AI** environment, including working with **Gemini models** and multimodal AI. ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][1])

Learners explore how to craft effective prompts, guide generative AI output, and apply image analysis techniques to inform prompt design. ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][1])

The course includes hands-on labs and a **challenge lab** to assess your prompt design skills under real conditions. ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][2])

**Duration:** ~1 hour 45 minutes ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][1])
**Level:** Introductory ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][1])

---

### üéØ Learning Objectives

By completing this course, participants will be able to:

1. Gain foundational understanding of **generative AI** and prompt engineering. ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][1])
2. Design effective prompts for **Gemini models** (text, image, multimodal). ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][1])
3. Use **Vertex AI Studio** to prototype generative AI workflows. ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][3])
4. Work with **image analysis and multimodal inputs** to enrich prompt outcomes. ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][1])
5. Apply prompt design techniques in a **challenge lab** setting to test your knowledge. ([Google Cloud Skills Boost][2])

